Colors_Step.query: a = load "${App.Datasets.rplcm_salesrepopportunity_dataset.Alias}"; a = group a by all; a = foreach a generate (case when {{coalesce(column(Details_Close_Won.result, ["sum_percent"]), 0).asObject()}} > 0 then "#067D1E" when {{coalesce(column(Details_Close_Won.result, ["sum_percent"]), 0).asObject()}} < 0 then "#E3193B" else "#192B61" end) as 'Diff_Close_Won', (case when {{coalesce(column(Details_Quota_Attainment.result, ["sum_percent"]), 0).asObject()}} > 0 then "#067D1E" when {{coalesce(column(Details_Quota_Attainment.result, ["sum_percent"]), 0).asObject()}} < 0 then "#E3193B" else "#192B61" end) as 'Diff_Quota_Attainment', (case when {{coalesce(column(Details_Win_Rate.result, ["sum_percent"]), 0).asObject()}} > 0 then "#067D1E" when {{coalesce(column(Details_Win_Rate.result, ["sum_percent"]), 0).asObject()}} < 0 then "#E3193B" else "#192B61" end) as 'Diff_Win_Rate', (case when {{coalesce(column(Details_Avg_Sales_Cycle.result, ["sum_percent"]), 0).asObject()}} > 0 then "#067D1E" when {{coalesce(column(Details_Avg_Sales_Cycle.result, ["sum_percent"]), 0).asObject()}} < 0 then "#E3193B" else "#192B61" end) as 'Diff_Avg_Sales_Cycle';

KPI_Avg_Sales_Cycle.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.rplcm_salesrepopportunity_dataset.Alias}"; q = filter q by {{column(Leaderboard.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field")}}; q = filter q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsClosed_Field'== "true" ; q = filter q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsWon_Field' == "true" ;  q = group q by all; q = foreach q generate coalesce((sum('RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_CloseDate_Field_day_epoch') - sum('RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedCreatedDate_Field_day_epoch'))/count(),0) as 'sum_Days_Open';

Leaderboard.query: u = load "${App.Datasets.user.Alias}"; a = load "${App.Datasets.rplcm_salesrepopportunity_dataset.Alias}"; q = filter a by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsWon_Field' == "true"; r = filter a by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsClosed_Field' == "true"; Avg_Day = filter a by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsClosed_Field' == "true" && 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsWon_Field' == "true"; OpptyCount_Left = filter a by  {{cell(dropdown_measure_one.selection,0, "filter").asObject()}}; OpptyCount_Right = filter a by {{cell(dropdown_measure_two.selection,0, "filter").asObject()}}; AvgDeal_Left = filter a by  {{cell(dropdown_measure_one.selection,0, "filter").asObject()}}; AvgDeal_Right = filter a by {{cell(dropdown_measure_two.selection,0, "filter").asObject()}}; leftpipe = filter a by  {{cell(dropdown_measure_one.selection,0, "filter").asObject()}}; rightpipe = filter a by {{cell(dropdown_measure_two.selection,0, "filter").asObject()}}; Activities = load "${App.Datasets.activity.Alias}"; Activities = group Activities by ('Owner.UniqueUserName', 'IsClosed'); Activities = foreach Activities generate 'Owner.UniqueUserName' as 'Owner.UniqueUserName', 'IsClosed' as 'IsClosed', count() as 'count'; Completed_Activities = filter Activities by 'IsClosed' == "true"; Percentage = group Completed_Activities by 'Owner.UniqueUserName' full, Activities by 'Owner.UniqueUserName'; Percentage = foreach Percentage generate Activities['Owner.UniqueUserName'] as 'Owner.UniqueUserName', coalesce( sum(Completed_Activities['count']) / sum(Activities['count']), 0) as 'CompletedRate'; Percentage_Left = group Completed_Activities by 'Owner.UniqueUserName' full, Activities by 'Owner.UniqueUserName'; Percentage_Left = foreach Percentage_Left generate Activities['Owner.UniqueUserName'] as 'Owner.UniqueUserName', coalesce( sum(Completed_Activities['count']) / sum(Activities['count']), 0) as 'CompletedRate_Left'; quota = load "${App.Datasets.quota.Alias}"; u = filter u by 'IsActive' == "true"; c = group u by 'UniqueUserName' full, OpptyCount_Left by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, OpptyCount_Right by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, AvgDeal_Right by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, AvgDeal_Left by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full ,q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, r by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, quota by 'User.UniqueUserName' full, Avg_Day by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, leftpipe by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, rightpipe by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, Percentage by 'Owner.UniqueUserName' full, Percentage_Left by 'Owner.UniqueUserName'; c = foreach c generate coalesce(first(u['UniqueUserName']), first(q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field']), first(AvgDeal_Left['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field']),  first(AvgDeal_Right['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field']), first(OpptyCount_Right['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field']), first(OpptyCount_Left['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field']), first(r['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field']), first(quota['User.UniqueUserName']), first(Avg_Day['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field']), first(Percentage['Owner.UniqueUserName']), first(Percentage_Left['Owner.UniqueUserName'])) as 'UniqueUserName',  coalesce(sum(q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0) as 'sum_RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field',   (coalesce(sum(AvgDeal_Left['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0) / coalesce(count(OpptyCount_Left),0))  as 'sum_left_DealAmount',  (coalesce(sum(AvgDeal_Right['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0) / coalesce(count(OpptyCount_Right),0)) as 'sum_right_DealAmount', coalesce(count(OpptyCount_Left),0) as 'sum_left_count', coalesce(count(OpptyCount_Right),0) as 'sum_right_count', coalesce(sum(leftpipe['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0) as 'sum_pipe', coalesce(sum(rightpipe['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0) as 'sum_pipe_right', coalesce((sum(Avg_Day['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_CloseDate_Field_day_epoch']) - sum(Avg_Day['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedCreatedDate_Field_day_epoch']))/count(Avg_Day),0) as 'sum_DaysOpen',  coalesce(sum(q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) / sum(r['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0) as 'sum_win_rate', coalesce(sum(Percentage_Left['CompletedRate_Left']),0) as 'sum_LeftActivity', coalesce(sum(Percentage['CompletedRate']),0) as 'sum_RightActivity',   coalesce(sum(q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) / sum(quota['QuotaAmount']),0) as 'sum_QuotaAmount'; c = foreach c generate 'UniqueUserName' as 'UniqueUserName', {{cell(dropdown_measure_one.selection,0, "first_f").asObject()}}, {{cell(dropdown_measure_two.selection,0, "first_f").asObject()}}; c = order c by ('{{cell(dropdown_measure_one.selection,0, "left").asObject()}}' desc nulls last, '{{cell(dropdown_measure_two.selection,0, "right").asObject()}}' desc nulls last);

User_Count.query: u = load "${App.Datasets.user.Alias}"; u = group u by all; u = foreach u generate count() as 'count';

KPI_Quota_Attainment.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.rplcm_salesrepopportunity_dataset.Alias}"; q = filter q by {{column(Leaderboard.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field")}}; q = filter q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsWon_Field' == "true"; quota = load "${App.Datasets.quota.Alias}"; quota = filter quota by{{column(Leaderboard.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("User.UniqueUserName")}}; u = load "${App.Datasets.user.Alias}"; u = filter u by {{column(Leaderboard.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("UniqueUserName")}}; c = group u by 'UniqueUserName' full, q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, quota by 'User.UniqueUserName'; c = foreach c generate coalesce(u['UniqueUserName'], q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field'], quota['User.UniqueUserName']) as 'UniqueUserName', coalesce(sum(q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0) as 'sum_RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field', coalesce(sum(quota['QuotaAmount']),0) as 'sum_QuotaAmount'; c = group c by all; c = foreach c generate coalesce(sum('sum_RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field') / sum('sum_QuotaAmount'),0) as 'sum_quota_attainment';

Details_Avg_Sales_Cycle.query: Sales_Cycle = load "${App.Datasets.rplcm_salesrepopportunity_dataset.Alias}"; Sales_Cycle = filter Sales_Cycle by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsClosed_Field'== "true" ; Sales_Cycle = filter Sales_Cycle by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsWon_Field' == "true" ;  Avg_Day = group Sales_Cycle by ('RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field'); Avg_Day = foreach Avg_Day generate 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' as 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field', coalesce((sum('RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_CloseDate_Field_day_epoch') - sum('RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedCreatedDate_Field_day_epoch'))/count(),0) as 'avg_Days_Open'; u = load "${App.Datasets.user.Alias}"; c = group u by 'UniqueUserName' full, Avg_Day by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field'; c = foreach c generate coalesce(u['UniqueUserName'], Avg_Day['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field']) as 'UniqueUserName', sum(Avg_Day['avg_Days_Open']) as 'avg_Days_Open', avg(sum(Avg_Day['avg_Days_Open'])) over([-1000..1000] partition by all order by sum(Avg_Day['avg_Days_Open']) asc ) as 'avg_Days_Open_Total', rank() over([..] partition by all order by sum(Avg_Day['avg_Days_Open']) asc ) as 'sum_Rank'; c = group c by 'UniqueUserName'; c = foreach c generate 'UniqueUserName', sum('sum_Rank') as 'sum_Rank', sum('avg_Days_Open') as 'avg_Days_Open', sum('avg_Days_Open_Total') as 'avg_Days_Open_Total', (-1 * (sum('avg_Days_Open') - sum('avg_Days_Open_Total')) / sum('avg_Days_Open_Total')) as 'sum_percent'; c = filter c by {{column(Leaderboard.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("UniqueUserName")}}; c = group c by all; c = foreach c generate (case when count() == 1 then first('sum_percent') else 0 end) as 'sum_percent', (case when count() == 1 then first('sum_Rank') else 1 end) as 'sum_Rank';

Details_Close_Won.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.rplcm_salesrepopportunity_dataset.Alias}"; q = filter q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsWon_Field' == "true"; u = load "${App.Datasets.user.Alias}"; c = group u by 'UniqueUserName' full, q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field'; c = foreach c generate coalesce(u['UniqueUserName'], q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field']) as 'UniqueUserName', coalesce(sum(q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0) as 'sum_RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field', avg(coalesce(sum(q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0)) over([-1000..1000] partition by all order by coalesce(sum(q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0) desc) as 'avg_Amount_Total', rank() over([..] partition by all order by coalesce(sum(q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0) desc) as 'sum_Rank'; c = group c by 'UniqueUserName'; c = foreach c generate 'UniqueUserName', sum('sum_RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field') as 'sum_RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field', sum('avg_Amount_Total') as 'avg_Amount_Total', sum('sum_Rank') as 'sum_Rank', (sum('sum_RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field') - sum('avg_Amount_Total')) / sum('avg_Amount_Total') as 'sum_percent'; c = filter c by {{column(Leaderboard.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("UniqueUserName")}}; c = group c by all; c = foreach c generate (case when count() == 1 then first('sum_percent') else 0 end) as 'sum_percent',(case when count() == 1 then first('sum_Rank') else 1 end) as 'sum_Rank';

Details_Quota_Attainment.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.rplcm_salesrepopportunity_dataset.Alias}"; q = filter q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsWon_Field' == "true"; quota = load "${App.Datasets.quota.Alias}"; u = load "${App.Datasets.user.Alias}"; c = group u by 'UniqueUserName' full, q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field', quota by 'User.UniqueUserName'; c = foreach c generate coalesce(u['UniqueUserName'], q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field'], quota['User.UniqueUserName']) as 'UniqueUserName', coalesce((sum(q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) /sum(quota['QuotaAmount']) * 100),0) as 'sum_QuotaAmount'; c = group c by 'UniqueUserName'; c = foreach c generate 'UniqueUserName', sum('sum_QuotaAmount') as 'sum_QuotaAmount', avg(sum('sum_QuotaAmount')) over([-1000..1000] partition by all order by sum('sum_QuotaAmount') desc ) as 'avg_QuotaAmount_Total', rank() over([..] partition by all order by sum('sum_QuotaAmount') desc ) as 'sum_Rank'; c = group c by 'UniqueUserName'; c = foreach c generate 'UniqueUserName', sum('sum_Rank') as 'sum_Rank', sum('sum_QuotaAmount') as 'sum_QuotaAmount', sum('avg_QuotaAmount_Total') as 'avg_QuotaAmount_Total', (sum('sum_QuotaAmount') - sum('avg_QuotaAmount_Total')) / sum('avg_QuotaAmount_Total') as 'sum_percent'; c = filter c by {{column(Leaderboard.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("UniqueUserName")}}; c = group c by all; c = foreach c generate (case when count() == 1 then first('sum_percent') else 0 end) as 'sum_percent', (case when count() == 1 then first('sum_Rank') else 1 end) as 'sum_Rank';

Team_Compare_Table.query: u = load "${App.Datasets.user.Alias}"; q = load "${App.Datasets.rplcm_salesrepopportunity_dataset.Alias}"; won = filter q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsWon_Field' == "true"; commit = filter q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedForecastCategory_Field' =="Forecast"; bestcase =  filter q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedForecastCategory_Field' =="BestCase"; pipeline = filter q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedForecastCategory_Field' =="Pipeline"; Forecast = filter q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsWon_Field' == "true" || ('RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsClosed_Field' == "false" && !('RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedForecastCategory_Field' in ["Omitted","Closed"])); quota = load "${App.Datasets.quota.Alias}"; u = filter u by 'IsActive' == "true"; c = group u by 'UniqueUserName' full, won by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, commit by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, bestcase by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, pipeline by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, Forecast by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full, quota by 'User.UniqueUserName'; c = foreach c generate coalesce(u['UniqueUserName'], won['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field'], quota['User.UniqueUserName'], commit['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field'], bestcase['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field'], pipeline['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field']) as 'UniqueUserName', (case when (coalesce(sum(quota['QuotaAmount']),0) - coalesce(sum(won['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0)) > 0 then (coalesce(sum(quota['QuotaAmount']),0) - coalesce(sum(won['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']),0)) else 0 end) as 'sum_Quota Remaining', sum(won['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) as 'sum_Won', sum(commit['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) as 'sum_Commit' , sum(bestcase['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) as 'sum_Best Case', sum(pipeline['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) as 'sum_Pipeline' , sum(Forecast['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) as 'sum_Forecast';

Details_Win_Rate.query: x = load "${App.Datasets.rplcm_salesrepopportunity_dataset.Alias}"; q = filter x by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsWon_Field' == "true"; r = filter x by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_PrefixedIsClosed_Field' == "true"; u = load "${App.Datasets.user.Alias}"; c = group u by 'UniqueUserName' full, q by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field' full,r by 'RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field'; c = foreach c generate coalesce(u['UniqueUserName'], q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field'], r['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_Owner_UniqueUserName_Field']) as 'UniqueUserName', coalesce((sum(q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) /(sum(r['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field']) + sum(q['RPLCM_SalesRepOpportunity_GrainAmount_Field'])) * 100),0) as 'sum_WinRate'; c = group c by 'UniqueUserName'; c = foreach c generate 'UniqueUserName', sum('sum_WinRate') as 'sum_WinRate', avg(sum('sum_WinRate')) over([-1000..1000] partition by all order by sum('sum_WinRate') desc) as 'avg_WinRate_Total', rank() over([..] partition by all order by sum('sum_WinRate') desc) as 'sum_Rank'; c = group c by 'UniqueUserName'; c = foreach c generate 'UniqueUserName', sum('sum_Rank') as 'sum_Rank', sum('sum_WinRate') as 'sum_WinRate', sum('avg_WinRate_Total') as 'avg_WinRate_Total', (sum('sum_WinRate') - sum('avg_WinRate_Total')) / sum('avg_WinRate_Total') as 'sum_percent'; c = filter c by {{column(Leaderboard.selection, ["UniqueUserName"]).asEquality("UniqueUserName")}}; c = group c by all; c = foreach c generate (case when count() == 1 then first('sum_percent') else 0 end) as 'sum_percent', (case when count() == 1 then first('sum_Rank') else 1 end) as 'sum_Rank';

parameters.text: Metrics are compared to team average
